block body
  section.media
    .container.content-wrap
      .row
        .col-sm-12
          h1.space Kate in the Media

      .row
        .col-sm-8
          p.
            Keep up with Kate as she does interviews, articles,
            forums, and generally moves about town!

  section.endorsements
    .container.content-wrap
      .row
        .col-sm-12
          h2 Endorsements
          blockquote
            p
              strong.
                "I wholeheartedly endorse the candidacy of Attorney Kate Dyer for
                Circuit Court Judge. Ms. Dyer has been a City Judge for the Town
                of Coopertown for the past six years. During this time she has
                administered the law with high integrity, fairness and
                professionalism."

          cite
            p
              em Sam Childs
            p Mayor of Coopertown, Tennessee
  section
    .container.content-wrap
      .row
        .col-sm-12
          h2 Print Media
          blockquote
            p
              strong.
                "Kate Dyer, who has more than 25 years of experience as a
                prosecutor and defense attorney, said she is more qualified,
                having served as a judge in Coopertown for the past six years."
          cite
            p
              em The Leaf Chronicle, July 3 2014
            p
              a(target="_blank", href="http://www.theleafchronicle.com/article/20140622/NEWS01/306210038/Judge-hopefuls-want-more-efficiency-from-courts") "Judge hopefuls want more efficiency from courts"

